  schema:name "Autonomous Worlds: Persistent Virtual Economies on Blockchain" ;
  schema:description "The vision of autonomous worlds as persistent, permissionlessly-extensible virtual environments where game state, rules, and ownership are enshrined on public blockchains. Covers permanence, interoperability, community control, and what distinguishes them from traditional games." ;
